        <abstract>
            <p>Starts tomorrow for visit to Farrer and Effie [Euphemia Farrer, daughter of Hensleigh Wedgwood]. Has not done such a feat [i.e., staying as a guest of someone outside the immediate family?] for 25 years.</p> 
<p>Has been half killing himself with <hi rend="italic">Drosera</hi>.</p> 
        </abstract>
